(1, 'upload/thumbnails/202211070950dhss1.jpg', '<p>A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step. - Confucius Ripumardini Sainik Secondary School was established under the aegis of Nepali Army Welfare Fund and in the Patronship of Nepali Army Wives&rsquo; Association (NAWA) on 6th Falgun, 2061. The school was solely founded to impart the quality education for the offspring of Nepali Army (both serving and former staff) and to the children of civilians. The education of the 21st Century has been assured to provide the children in the school. The First Batch of SLC graduated in 2069 B.S. RSMV has widened the horizon of imparting quality education by commencing the 10+2 Program in Science under the Higher Secondary Education Board (HSEB) in 2073 B.S. In the 15 years of the school&rsquo;s establishment, we want to gloriously mention that we achieved the marvelous results both in academic as well as extra-curricular activities. Our beautiful minds of the school performed their excellency in the national and international forums of competition. We do not believe only in educating the children about the textbooks, we rather believe in facilitating them from the multiple aspects of life. We are not merely teaching a child rather we are teaching a child who is retrieving ample information through different dimensions of life. We believe in providing them a complete environment where s/he can visualize numerous aspects where he can accommodate himself with any obscure modes of life. We think education is a road to march for the competency of the learners where they can find themselves in the comfortable zone to learn even in any sort of complexities. So it is to empower them. It is our attempt to rather revitalize, reenergize and refresh them with the new course of practicality, creativity and productivity. In the long mission of achieving the wonderful results, there is of course, the immense hand, mind and soul of many creative persons. We happened to meet many ups and downs to get this success of today. We know behind every achievement, there is great effort the sound team work of the school and very friendly education provided here. I acclaim that both the teachers and students feel this holy place as their warm home but not simply as a school to study only. We agree in the doctrine of minimization of cost and maximization of quality rather. The tasks, we perform in volume, less matters than that of the task we strive for the value. So, I pursue the value in the every deeds either that is in the classroom or beyond the classroom. Either that is in personal life or professional, the value is counted precious ever. Yes, this is the age of adding value in the every deeds. The education system of the nation should foster the daily life of people as education is directly proportional to life. Education should be the throb of our culture, technology and day to day activities of life. Education should connect the life people in their real life situations. So, We believe in providing the education to enrich the life of students from different dimensions.</p>', '<p>our mission is&nbsp;<strong>mission</strong></p>', '<p>our vision is&nbsp;<strong>haha</strong></p>', NULL, '2022-12-21 01:18:07');
